Day 18 — Power Query

Power Query is a data transformation tool that allows users to efficiently extract, transform, and load (ETL) data from multiple sources into a structured format for analysis and reporting.

🔹 ETL Process

Extract — Gather data from various sources

Transform — Clean and reshape the data

Load — Import data into the destination system

🔹 Why Use Power Query

Automation of ETL processes: Streamlines data extraction, transformation, and loading

Reproducibility: Ensures consistent results by applying the same transformations across datasets

Scalability: Can work with datasets exceeding Excel’s 1 million row limit

✅ Key takeaway: Power Query simplifies and automates data preparation for analysis.